y nos cambiamos.

257
00:19:23,132 --> 00:19:24,281
Perdonadme.

258
00:19:24,692 --> 00:19:26,683
Perdonad mi atrevimiento.

259
00:19:27,452 --> 00:19:28,487
Soy Orestes,

260
